1–2, Pronotum (1, lateral view; 2, dorsal view); 3, Fastigium of vertex (dorsal view); 4, Ovipositor (lateral view); 5. Female cerci (lateral view); 6, Female subgenital plate (ventral view); 7, Male subgenital plate (ventral view); 8, Male apical and subapical segments of maxillary palpi (lateral view); 9, Male posterior abdomen and cerci (dorsal view). scale bars = 1mm.
</paragraph>
